         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3173_0067"/>Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Wien</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">XVIII. Spöttelga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3173_0066"/><hi rend="pre-print">Das <hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb324"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11461">Göthe</rs>-Haus</rs></hi>.</hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11461">Goethe</rs></hi>.</hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb146">Frankfurt a.M.</rs></hi></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3173_0066"/><date when="1903-12-30">30. 12. 03</date>.</dateline></opener><p>Ich wün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che Dir, <salute>mein lieber Freund,</salute> Deiner <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Frau</rs> und Deinem <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb12692">Sohn</rs> ein glückliches neues <date when="1904">Jahr</date>.</p><closer>Dein getreuer <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann.</signed></closer><postscript><p><handShift scribe="#pmb23674"/>Herzlichen Gruß!</p></postscript></div>
      </body>
